**Audience blind spots:**
- Nobody explains that the tip chips faster than a full coverage nail — and how to counter this (capping the free edge with top coat)
- The actual cost difference between DIY and salon for this specific look is never broken down
- The short-nail suitability answer is almost always "yes" but competitors never explain *why* (the tip proportion rule)

